definitions.definition: A board game for two players , each beginning with sixteen chess pieces moving according to fixed rules across a chessboard with the objective to checkmate the opposing king .

main_definition: A board game for two players , each beginning with sixteen chess pieces moving according to fixed rules across a chessboard with the objective to checkmate the opposing king .

definitions.definition: ( now chiefly US ) Any of several species of grass in the genus Bromus , generally considered weeds .

main_definition: ( now chiefly US ) Any of several species of grass in the genus Bromus , generally considered weeds .

definitions.definition: One of the platforms , consisting of two or more planks dowelled together, for the flooring of a temporary military bridge .

main_definition: ( military , chiefly in the plural ) One of the platforms , consisting of two or more planks dowelled together, for the flooring of a temporary military bridge .
